指標，並說明我國再犯風險評估在社區處遇中的應用實務。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7c052f4dd83e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114120", "c": "114", "s": "0702", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "犯罪學與再犯預測", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "四", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "監獄官"}'::jsonb, NULL),
